<div id="review_2651553930" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2651553930" />
    <a title="Connie F" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/57189150-connie-f"><img alt="Connie F" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2651553930?book_show_action=true">Jan 01, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Connie F" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Connie F" href="/user/show/57189150-connie-f">Connie F</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2651553930" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11920469638384068710">This series is full of fascinating historical research. I feel that I have been there and lived with these wonderful characters. There is definite clear and uncompromising religious ideas woven through and integral to the plot. I found it worthy of the understanding for the characters. Many if my God ideas are similar, so I enjoyed this aspect as well. Well written. Intricate in plot, and often surprising. And that whole nest historical information touch. Worth the read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


